Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on April 01, 2014 Description from Terminal Escape:
A first person dub of a nine song INSTED banger, taped over a screaming live HÜSKER DÜ set (that honestly got me more stoked than the INSTED shits). Slick and energetic late '80s straight edge hardcore, but you probably already knew that. This band travels the 7 SECONDS to UNIFORM CHOICE road more than the MINOR THREAT to YOUTH OF TODAY highway...no song titles, I'll leave that (and perhaps the actual source of these jammers and whether or not they are available elsewhere) to the true hardcores. AT LAST
